c492d4b.mp4?t=1762605562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/cb2844e4144d9ddd255fbdc251ae894e.webp?t=1762605562\" width=334 height=23 /></span><br>Buy new ships and customize their loadout weapon by weapon, create a flexible fleet fitting multiple roles based on your needs, or commit your fleet to a specific task and playstyle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/0839c9c7ce1cffb57ed3356d41ab9d03.poster.avif?t=1762605562\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/0839c9c7ce1cffb57ed3356d41ab9d03.webm?t=1762605562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/0839c9c7ce1cffb57ed3356d41ab9d03.mp4?t=1762605562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/a2a403192320869004fcb9b56473ef89.webp?t=1762605562\" width=330 height=23 /></span><br>Complete randomized contracts of various types in gradually more difficult sectors.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/de69acafb80ae1910ff074665f2011e6.poster.avif?t=1762605562\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/de69acafb80ae1910ff074665f2011e6.webm?t=1762605562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/de69acafb80ae1910ff074665f2011e6.mp4?t=1762605562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/c9e79db300bba49353586dd531f85649.webp?t=1762605562\" width=334 height=25 /></span><br>Capture Control Points and build defenses in more complex Conquest sectors which require a more strategic approach<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/c7e8d202b2d1bf1d129bb6dff2fd3c24.poster.avif?t=1762605562\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/c7e8d202b2d1bf1d129bb6dff2fd3c24.webm?t=1762605562\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1762570/extras/c7e8d202b2d1bf1d129bb6dff2fd3c24.mp4?t=1762605562\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Additional Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Conventional Weapons<br></li><li>Modular Damage<br></li><li>Dynamic Sector traffic<br></li><li>Detection Mechanics</li></ul>",
